HEADWORD: Doddart
<hw>Dod"dart</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A game much like
hockey, played in an open field; also, the, bent stick for playing the
game.</def> <mark>[Local, Eng.]</mark> <rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

